    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so heavy. like, does it even make sense to keep fighting when the person everyone knew is gone? i look at the life i'm supposed to be living and it just feels like a lie. it feels like i'm just taking up space in a world i don't belong to anymore.",
